cff-version: 1.2.0
title: HumanifyMe
message: "If you use HumanifyMe in your work, please cite it."
type: software
authors:
  - family-names: McQueary
    given-names: Joshua
url: "https://humanifyme.com"
repository-code: "https://github.com/JoshMcQ/HumanifyMe"
abstract: >-
  A local-first MCP server that learns one person's writing voice and rewrites
  AI-generated drafts in that voice. Writing samples stay on the user's machine;
  only redacted text reaches the configured LLM provider.
keywords:
  - mcp
  - model-context-protocol
  - writing-style
  - personalization
  - local-first
  - privacy
license: LicenseRef-source-available-with-MIT-core
version: 0.1.0
date-released: "2026-06-26"
